    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable driver for someone willing to put in a little TLC. While it remains mechanically functional and starts up without issue, it does show its age with some noticeable scratches on the body and some fading in the paint. The interior is intact but has visible wear on the upholstery and a few stains on the carpet. It currently runs and drives, though a prospective buyer should expect to address some minor suspension noise and standard maintenance items in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its history and is priced accordingly.",
