    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty! I\u2019m listing my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it is in pristine condition. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and still has that incredible fresh-car feel. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is definitely the one for you. Come swing by and take a look\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
