    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. This vehicle retains its original showroom luster, featuring flawless paintwork with no chips or swirl marks, complemented by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition; the leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or imperfections. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Accompanied by a comprehensive binder of service records from day one, original window sticker, and all keys. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key vehicle that needs absolutely nothing.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
